                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "rXGbW",
                      "name": "Editor Content",
                      "clip": true,
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "height": "fill_container",
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "gap": 20,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "0Vmqe",
                          "name": "p1",
                          "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "林远站在观测台上，透过巨大的舷窗望向外面的星空。这片星域完全陌生——没有任何一颗星星能与他记忆中的星图对应。",
                          "lineHeight": 2,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "w5Jxz",
                          "name": "p2",
                          "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "「导航系统还是没有恢复吗？」他问身后的苏晴。",
                          "lineHeight": 2,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "KSASr",
                          "name": "p3",
                          "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "苏晴摇了摇头，全息屏幕上的数据流在她脸上投下蓝色的光影。「主数据库的损坏比我们预想的严重得多。不只是导航数据，连船员档案都出现了大面积的数据缺失。」",
                          "lineHeight": 2,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "klEYb",
                          "name": "p4",
                          "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "content": "「也就是说，我们不知道自己是谁，也不知道自己在哪。」林远苦笑了一下。",
                          "lineHeight": 2,
                          "fontFamily": "Geist",
                          "fontSize": 15,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    }
                  ]
