                        {
                          "type": "frame",
                          "id": "oym0f",
                          "name": "Text Edit Area",
                          "clip": true,
                          "width": "fill_container",
                          "height": "fill_container",
                          "layout": "vertical",
                          "gap": 24,
                          "padding": [
                            24,
                            32
                          ],
                          "children": [
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "KwJik",
                              "name": "para1",
                              "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "意识像是从深海中缓缓浮起。",
                              "lineHeight": 2,
                              "fontFamily": "Geist",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "TImsK",
                              "name": "para2",
                              "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "林远睁开眼睛的那一刻，看到的是一片纯白的天花板。冰冷的空气灌入肺部，带着一股消毒水和金属混合的气味。他试图动弹，却发现四肢僵硬得像是被冻住了一般。",
                              "lineHeight": 2,
                              "fontFamily": "Geist",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "Tr6WX",
                              "name": "para3",
                              "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "「冬眠舱解冻程序完成。」一个没有感情的电子声在耳边响起，「请保持静止，系统正在进行生命体征检测。」",
                              "lineHeight": 2,
                              "fontFamily": "Geist",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "frame",
                              "id": "K2MsR",
                              "name": "Cursor Line",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "children": [
                                {
                                  "type": "text",
                                  "id": "7krA5",
                                  "name": "textBeforeCursor",
                                  "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                                  "content": "冬眠舱？林远皱起眉头，脑海中一片混沌。他记得自己……他记得什么？",
                                  "lineHeight": 2,
                                  "fontFamily": "Geist",
                                  "fontSize": 15,
                                  "fontWeight": "normal"
                                },
                                {
                                  "type": "rectangle",
                                  "cornerRadius": 1,
                                  "id": "Niqrk",
                                  "name": "cursor",
                                  "fill": "#3B82F6",
                                  "width": 2,
                                  "height": 22
                                }
                              ]
                            },
                            {
                              "type": "text",
                              "id": "vabvB",
                              "name": "para5",
                              "fill": "#F0F0F5",
                              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                              "width": "fill_container",
                              "content": "他记得一艘船。一艘很大的船。还有星星——无数的星星，在舷窗外静静地燃烧。但除此之外，一切都是模糊的，像是隔着一层毛玻璃去看过去的自己。",
                              "lineHeight": 2,
                              "fontFamily": "Geist",
                              "fontSize": 15,
                              "fontWeight": "normal"
                            }
                          ]
                        },
